# Aaron System Utility (ASU)

A professional, modular Windows maintenance and diagnostics utility written in PowerShell 5.1.

## Features
- Hardware diagnostics
- Memory analysis
- Storage health monitoring
- Startup management
- Network diagnostics
- Battery analysis
- Windows repair tools
- System cleanup
- HTML reports
- Comprehensive logging

## Getting Started
1. Download the repository.
2. Run `ASU.bat` as Administrator for full functionality.
3. Navigate the menu-driven interface.

## Requirements
- Windows 11 / Windows 10
- PowerShell 5.1

